dct_title_s: Nouvelle Hollande (à présent Nouvelle-York), Nouvelle-Angleterre, et une partie de la Virginie
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Described by Campbell as second state of Ogilby's Novi Belgii, quod nunc Novi Jorck vocatur, Novae q[ue] Angliae & partis Virginiae. Probably issued in: La galerie agreable du monde. Leiden : Pierre vander Aa, [1729?] Prime meridian: Ferro. Includes ill.
